Trait

 View source
  • View history
  • Talk (0)

Traits are a key gameplay mechanic in Halls of Torment, providing Heroes with various buffs.

Elemental Surge (Fire)
I 30 Transforms damage of summons to fire.
Gives a 10% chance to burn on hit.
Horde Summons are excluded.
Elemental Surge (Lightning)
I 30 Transforms damage of summons to lightning.
Gives a 10% chance to electrify on hit.
Horde Summons are excluded.
Elemental Surge (Ice)
 I 30 Transforms damage of summons to ice.
Gives a 10% chance to frost on hit.
Horde Summons are excluded.

    +5% Damage (Frost)
    +5% Frost Damage
    +10% Frost Chance

Ability Trait

Ability Traits improve the effectiveness of abilities, possibly at a compromise.

For each trait level, the hero must be at a certain level for it to be displayed in the selection pool. Below is the full list.

Trait Level I II III IV V VI VII VIII IX X
Hero Level 8 16 24 32 40 48 56 64 72 80
